description: We're taking the HIGHlight of your week to the next level. Our most anticipated episode is here and just in time for the holidays! HAPPY 4/20 lil' nuggets! Our heart rates are up and views are down, we're giving the people what they want. All of life's most important, unanswered questions you JUANA know are debunked. What's the biggest color? What exactly IS a salad? Are bugs considered zoo animals? You're about to find out. Soar with us as we overthink...under the influence. Enjoy this weeks good good episode ;)
